trailingComments.value:
*
 * Extract a block from a matrix 
 * 
 * @export
 * @param {Array} x
 * @param {Array} from from position
 * @param {Array} to to position
 * @returns {Array}
 * @example
 * 
 * getBlock([[1,2,3],
 *           [3,4,5]], [0,0], [1,1])
 * // [[1, 2],
 *     [3, 4]]
